Text: does it have an album cover for iphones?
nah, but you can add it by yourself.. just go to Google.Com and download .jpeg file of the cover and go to iTunes and then add it. Piece of cake :)

It's a pity the sound quality is degraded by using VBR AND the worst of the 3 MP3 formats, Joint Stereo, which isn't actually even stereo at all. Proper stereo is better, but still not right, the ONLY way to get 2 separate left & right channels is Dual Stereo/Dual Channel.
Thanks for sharing though, looking for a wav or flac version.
